stateDiagram-v2
    %% Manual Summary - State Machine Diagram
    %% Based on actual ManualSummary.tsx implementation

    [*] --> CLOSED

    %% Transitions with method scopes
    CLOSED --> GENERATING : ManualSummary.generate()\n[component mounts]
    
    GENERATING --> DISPLAYED : generateManualSummary()\n[relevantMessages.length > 0]
    GENERATING --> NO_MESSAGES : generateManualSummary()\n[relevantMessages.length === 0]
    
    DISPLAYED --> GENERATING : ManualSummary.handlePreset()\n[time range changes]
    
    NO_MESSAGES --> GENERATING : ManualSummary.handlePreset()\n[time range changes]
    
    %% Close transitions (available from any open state)
    GENERATING --> CLOSED : ManualSummary.onClose()\n[Escape key or backdrop click]
    DISPLAYED --> CLOSED : ManualSummary.onClose()\n[Escape key or backdrop click]
    NO_MESSAGES --> CLOSED : ManualSummary.onClose()\n[Escape key or backdrop click]

    %% Legend
    note right of CLOSED
        **State Definitions:**
        CLOSED: Modal closed, no processing
        GENERATING: Modal open, processing summary
        DISPLAYED: Modal open, showing summary
        NO_MESSAGES: Modal open, no messages found
        
        **Transition Format:**
        Component.method() [condition]
    end note
